# Frontend TypeScript

## Layout

- App Router pages: `frontend/app/`
- Feature logic: `frontend/features/` (show, inszenierung, debate, etc.)
- API clients: `frontend/lib/api/`
- Types: `frontend/lib/types/`
- Shared text utils: `frontend/lib/text/`

## Tests

- Vitest: `make test-frontend` or `cd frontend && npm test -- --run`
- Test files: `*.test.ts` next to source or under `frontend/lib/`

## Teil 2 playback

- Master playback: `frontend/features/inszenierung/teil2TextSyncPlayback.ts`
- Timing changes must align with backend `Teil2PerformancePlan` and pass `teil2TextSyncPlayback.test.ts`
- Do not add direct OSC calls outside established playback paths

## API

- Use typed clients in `frontend/lib/api/` — do not scatter raw fetch URLs
- Match backend schemas in `frontend/lib/types/`

## Sentence split

For Teil 2, keep `frontend/lib/text/splitSentences.ts` aligned with `backend/app/services/text_split.py`.
